title: mRNA ‘Vaccinated’ YouTube Content Creator Physics Girl (Dianna Cowern) Provides Another Health Update: “I am scared”
cleaned_text:
Yah! This is the most sore vaccine arm I’ve gotten. worth it 100 times over tho!

I can’t eat solid foods, or feed myself. I have moderate pain almost 24/7. I have trouble breathing and lose my ability to stay fully conscious when my symptoms intensify. I cannot leave the bed.

Y'know those arm workouts where you hold a 1 lb weight straight out, pulse, and it feels like literal torture? I feel like I did 500 of those.
